Changes to the sources should be documented here.  The format should
follow common "standards":  When recording changes in a ChangeLog, one
entry is made per person.  Logical changes are grouped together, while
logically distinct changes ("change sets") are separated by a single
blank line.  Entries should be brief, and should not explain why the
change has been made, only what the change was.  (The "why" can go in
the sources as a comment.)


